flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("", "6BD2FB2148DE244661543AB9DAADB7FF", "The Prime Kaahena of the Vaeulune community asks that all newcomers pay tribute to the ancient ancestors of the dunes by performing a Service ot the Past. With the blood of our foes we shall paint our destiny.")
mainObjectiveText: NSLOCTEXT("", "AD4AF2BD4EF0FE717EB85FB3EBF21DEC", "Kill threats in the batyards of the ruins. ")
